Plot: After a painful breakup, Ben develops insomnia. To kill time, he starts working the late night shift at the local supermarket, where his artistic imagination runs wild.
Title: Cashback
Actors: Michelle Ryan, Sean Biggerstaff, Erica Ellis, Jay Bowen
tomatoConsensus: An unlikable protagonist, messy editing, and gratuitous nudity might make audiences ask for their cash back.
